{"tid":193661,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【金像獎紅地氈】？？？「導彈胸」胸贏周秀娜","createTime":"2017-04-09T12:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T13:28:56.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac87b4ef58de0de4e5190399338257300cc5466","tid":193661,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCs8S3v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCs8S3v.jpg&h=cc44bb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【今日直擊】《第三十六屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮》今晚隆重舉行，出席的嘉賓陸續亮相紅地氈，由於天氣和暖，女星以性感打扮爭妍鬥麗。鄭欣宜﹑周秀娜「胸」降紅地氈，欣宜身穿性感花裙，其「導彈胸」相當誇張，胸贏娜姐；任達華和琦琦夫婦，負責頒最佳衣著獎，琦琦表示與老公眼光一致，評選準則是穿得有型及著得靚！<br />\n<br />\n今晚頒獎禮司儀鄭中基與太太余思敏拍拖亮相，余思敏亦罕有地低胸打扮示人；楊淇行紅地氈時險絆倒，幸王宗堯扶住她。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）"},{"pid":"d633732bf353b99cba9a51e9c296b550eb1722f4","tid":193661,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"佢個個撚係胸呀<br />\n開瓶器黎"},{"pid":"8d781898dbc48300452a3dfd398e1358e09a3364","tid":193661,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc26593e3886872d8ffe0ae3dbb5722e9a6484dd","tid":193661,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"未入黎已經估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f48e6e9bd258f96a84169abe84bdbb8ecb28a39","tid":193661,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"